t/L%C3%BD-ch%E1%BB%A7-b%E1%BA%A1-c%C6%A1/K%C3%BD-thi/poem-pkfli__2LyPcZrhYmTQKoA">Ký thi - 寄詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-ch%E1%BB%A7-b%E1%BA%A1-c%C6%A1/author-DkFAJMliuB5BNOAocA-9_Q">Lý chủ bạ cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/%C3%94-Giang-H%E1%BA%A1ng-V%C5%A9-mi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-g0P9eMDogqMTsentlG2GMQ">Ô Giang Hạng Vũ miếu - 烏江項羽廟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/T%E1%BA%B7ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-39DMTk0IHWNZx8yk5k-jVg">Tặng hữu nhân - 贈友人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/T%E1%BA%BF-thi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%8Ba-v%C4%83n/poem-mgYAjQ2Q5NsDGZNtKtk96w">Tế thiên địa văn - 祭天地文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Tr%C3%AC-bi%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A3i-nguy%E1%BB%87t/poem-L649IhVDnrAp7biremEEOQ">Trì biên đãi nguyệt - 池邊待月</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-N%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PSgXCHLe22-Whw_BN8uK9A">Trương Ngọc Nương</a>)<br></div>	</div>
